<!--
  Westgate Market - the outdoor square just west of Ados west gate.
  This is a SKELETON MAP. Open it in Tiled, paint it with your project's
  tilesets (recommended: world1.png ground, buildings1.png stalls, etc.)
  to match Ados visually. The object layer below contains the working
  spawnpoints, signs, and exits the engine actually reads.

  Stalls (left column): weaponer, armorer, seamstress
  Stalls (right column): grocer, farmers market, gift
  Realtor: at the south side, by the gate to the home interiors.
  Farmer: next to the farmers market stall.
-->
